\pard\plain \ql\ltrch\loch {\f1\fs24\b0\i0\cf1 This widget allows the customer to change their mobile phone number in CIDM Neo. }{\f1\fs24\b0\i0\cf1 If the customer attempts to change the userId on an account that is not QGA they will receive an error. The customer must be logged in to perform this process.}
\par\plain {\f1\fs24\b0\i0\cf1 The customer is prompted to enter the new mobile number. The widget sends a code to the new mobile number to verify the mobile.}
\par\plain {\f1\fs24\b0\i0\cf1 Once the customer enters the code the mobile number is updated in CIDM Neo, and a confirmation email is sent.}}